INVESTMENT DISCLAIMER

This software produces technical signals based on public financial data and
the stage-analysis methodology of Stan Weinstein (1988). It does NOT provide
financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. No representation is made that
any account will or is likely to achieve profits or losses similar to those
shown. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Users are solely
responsible for their own investment decisions and should consult a licensed
financial advisor before acting on any output of this software.
